data.description: New construction Highland Homes "Lindsey II" READY FOR MOVE IN! Gorgeous 3/2/2 with a large 1/2 acre lot in the beautiful community of Tower Grove Estates. This NEW home includes Builder warranties and energy saving features. Builder offers closing cost assistance to buyers using their preferred lenders. Affordable down payment and finance programs for most budgets. Home qualifies for 0% down USDA loan. This beautiful home features a double-door front entry that opens into a spacious great room with volume ceilings. Popular split bedroom plan places the secondary bedrooms on the other side of the home. The kitchen has "Energy Star" Whirlpool dishwasher, beautiful crown molding, eat-in-nook fully open to the dining room and great room. Large walk-in closet in the master suite and luxury bath that includes dual vanities, linen closet, corner-style garden tub and upgraded tile shower. Tower Grove Estates makes the location ideal for Brandon and Tampa commuters. The community features 28 spacious home sites, averaging 1/2 acre-plus in size, for privacy and plenty of space between homes. Create your own home; Highland Homes offers homes in several beautiful communities throughout Tampa Bay and Central Florida. Choose from over 30 floor plans with hundreds of options to fit your personal style and priced for your budget. Please call listing agent for additional information or to view this property.
